race.comment: The $160,000 Listed Tattersall's Recognition Stakes. BOOMTOWN BOSS (9) goes well for rider Lang who has four wins and a placing from seven rides and looks to be back in good order with a strong first-up victory at Eagle Farm. Is yet to miss a quinella spot in three second-up attempts and is sure to play a major role in the finish. TUFF TU MUS (7) resumes here but has strung seven wins together on the bounce with five of those coming at this track. Has to be included. CIFRADO (1) wasn't disgraced in the Hunter last time out and should find this a touch easier. Presents some value. OUGHTON (2) should be at his top third up and is expected to be strong late.
